    "Stregobor""I saw it, Geralt, I saw it all in the crystal..."

# game/script.rpy:4704
translate English choice_talk_ef0eaf94:

    # "Stregobor""Невероятно. Сорокопутка мертвая."
    "Stregobor""Incredible. The shrike is dead."

# game/script.rpy:4705
translate English choice_talk_92eb5d9d:

    # "Stregobor""Совершенно."
    "Stregobor""Completely."

# game/script.rpy:4706
translate English choice_talk_ab46dcac:

    # "Геральт не ответил"
    "Geralt didn`t answer."

# game/script.rpy:4711
translate English choice_talk_f3536935:

    # "Stregobor""Ну, Геральт, иди за повозкой. "
    "Stregobor""Well, Geralt, go get the cart."

# game/script.rpy:4712
translate English choice_talk_08d16039:

    # "Stregobor""Возьмем ее в башню."
    "Stregobor""We`ll take it to the tower."

# game/script.rpy:4713
translate English choice_talk_c65723a5:

    # "Stregobor""Надо сделать вскрытие."
    "Stregobor""We need to do an autopsy."

# game/script.rpy:4714
translate English choice_talk_6541d967:

    # "Кто-то, незнакомый ведьмаку, сидящий внутри него, стиснул рукоять меча."
    "Someone unknown to the witcher, sitting inside him, gripped the hilt of the sword."

# game/script.rpy:4723
translate English choice_talk_99e642d1:

    # "Geralt""Только коснись ее, колдун, и твоя голова окажется на брусчатке."
    "Geralt""Just touch it, sorcerer, and your head will be on the cobblestones."

# game/script.rpy:4732
translate English choice_talk_6c259545:

    # "Stregobor""Ты что, Геральт, спятил?"
    "Stregobor""Are you crazy, Geralt?"

# game/script.rpy:4733
translate English choice_talk_484dbf66:

    # "Stregobor""Да ты ранен, в шоке!"
    "Stregobor""You`re wounded, in shock!"

# game/script.rpy:4734
translate English choice_talk_a685c120:

    # "Stregobor""Вскрытие - единственный способ узнать..."
    "Stregobor""An autopsy is the only way to find out..."

# game/script.rpy:4743
translate English choice_talk_fc975c36:

    # "Geralt""Не прикасайся к ней!"
    "Geralt""Don`t touch her!"

# game/script.rpy:4752
translate English choice_talk_121a4b41:

    # "Stregobor""Хорошо!"
    "Stregobor""Fine!"

# game/script.rpy:4753
translate English choice_talk_545c39b9:

    # "Stregobor""Как хочешь!"
    "Stregobor""As you wish! "

# game/script.rpy:4754
translate English choice_talk_d6dabf9a:

    # "Stregobor""Но ты так никогда..."
    "Stregobor""But you will never..."

# game/script.rpy:4763
translate English choice_talk_c1e7f33e:

    # "Geralt""Прочь!"
    "Geralt""Away!"

# game/script.rpy:4772
translate English choice_talk_af8f4b74:

    # "Stregobor""Как хочешь. "
    "Stregobor""As you wish."

# game/script.rpy:4778
translate English choice_talk_cea7f3cf:

    # "Маг повернулся, ударил посохом в брусчатку."
    "The magician turned and struck the paving stones with his staff."

# game/script.rpy:4786
translate English choice_talk_59245d52:

    # "Mayor""Достаточно!!!"
    "Mayor""Enough!!! "

# game/script.rpy:4787
translate English choice_talk_305a47d6:

    # "Mayor""Кончайте мать вашу..."
    "Mayor""Finish your mother..."

# game/script.rpy:4788
translate English choice_talk_0f9a6b50:

    # "Ведьмак стоял неподвижно."
    "The Witcher stood motionless."

# game/script.rpy:4793
translate English choice_talk_aa04f2be:

    # "Войт подошел к нему."
    "The mayor approached him."

# game/script.rpy:4794
translate English choice_talk_a4fd586c:

    # "Mayor""Это все?"
    "Mayor""This is it?"

# game/script.rpy:4795
translate English choice_talk_807509e9:

    # "Mayor""Так оно выглядит - Меньшее Зло, которое ты выбрал?"
    "Mayor""Is this what it looks like - the Lesser Evil you have chosen?"

# game/script.rpy:4796
translate English choice_talk_0d11d546:

    # "Mayor""Ты сделал уже все, что считал нужным?"
    "Mayor""Have you done all you thought necessary?"

# game/script.rpy:4805
translate English choice_talk_70e6226d_1:

    # "Geralt""Да."
    "Geralt""Yes."

# game/script.rpy:4806
translate English choice_talk_f6449445:

    # "С трудом, не сразу ответил Геральт."
    "Geralt answered with difficulty and did not answer right away."

# game/script.rpy:4815
translate English choice_talk_ed871729:

    # "Mayor""Твоя рана серьезна?"
    "Mayor""Is your wound serious?"

# game/script.rpy:4824
translate English choice_talk_116c482b:

    # "Geralt""Нет."
    "Geralt""No."

# game/script.rpy:4833
translate English choice_talk_d7ddec3e:

    # "Mayor""В таком случае уходи отсюда."
    "Mayor""In that case, get out of here."

# game/script.rpy:4842
translate English choice_talk_70e6226d_2:

    # "Geralt""Да."
    "Geralt""Yes."

# game/script.rpy:4843
translate English choice_talk_b46f0d2c:

    # "Сказал ведьмак. "
    "The witcher said. "

# game/script.rpy:4849
translate English choice_talk_71bd7b83:

    # "Он еще минуту постоял, избегая взгляда войта. "
    "He stood there for another minute, avoiding the mayor`s gaze."

# game/script.rpy:4858
translate English choice_talk_16f6a09d:

    # "Потом медленно, очень медленно повернулся."
    "Then he turned around slowly, very slowly."

# game/script.rpy:4861
translate English choice_talk_7c8c8e14:

    # "Mayor""Геральт!"
    "Mayor""Geralt!"

# game/script.rpy:4864
translate English choice_talk_02b537e0:

    # "Ведьмак оглянулся."
    "The witcher looked back."

# game/script.rpy:4865
translate English choice_talk_55e5b7eb:

    # "Mayor""Не возвращайся сюда никогда."
    "Mayor""Don`t come back here ever. "

# game/script.rpy:4868
translate English choice_talk_97d16b08:

    # "Mayor""Никогда."
    "Mayor""Ever."

# game/script.rpy:4875
translate English choice_uti_6960e022:

    # "Что ему не следует лезть в чужие дела. "
    "That he shouldn`t meddle in other people`s affairs."

# game/script.rpy:4876
translate English choice_uti_7b2f98d8:

    # "В скором времени он собрал вещи. "
    "He soon packed his things."

# game/script.rpy:4877
translate English choice_uti_6c153b9d:

    # "И продолжил свой путь."
    "And continued on his way."

# game/script.rpy:4882
translate English choice_revenge_0c965c4a:

    # "Что он не допустит издевательств из-за чьих-то выдумок."
    "That he would not allow mockery because of someone`s inventions. "

# game/script.rpy:4883
translate English choice_revenge_0e129569:

    # "Ведьмак изначально считал проклятье Черного солнца бредом. "
    "The Witcher initially considered the curse of the Black Sun to be nonsense."

# game/script.rpy:4884
translate English choice_revenge_e8fe42be:

    # "Такие, как Стрегобор, заслуживают суда."
    "People like Stregobor deserve to be judged."

# game/script.rpy:4888
translate English choice_revenge_8fd1097b:

    # "Выходившего на улицу Геральта остановил войт."
    "Geralt, who was going out into the street, was stopped by the mayor."

# game/script.rpy:4893
translate English choice_revenge_1baf8bde:

    # "Mallet""Геральт, ты куда направился?"
    "Mallet""Geralt, where are you headed?"

# game/script.rpy:4898
translate English choice_revenge_174daca2:

    # "Geralt""Я к Стрегобору по делу."
    "Geralt""I`m going to see Stregobor on business."

# game/script.rpy:4899
translate English choice_revenge_100a2da5:

    # "Geralt""Личному."
    "Geralt""Personal."

# game/script.rpy:4900
translate English choice_revenge_ba3785c7:

    # "Сказал Геральт после недолгой паузы."
    "Geralt said after a short pause."

# game/script.rpy:4905
translate English choice_revenge_c485b281:

    # "Mallet""Я бы тоже сходил, мне надо посоветоваться с ним по поводу Ренфри."
    "Mallet""I would go too. I need to consult with him about Renfri."

# game/script.rpy:4910
translate English choice_revenge_ff942d17:

    # "Ведьмак понимал, что отвертеться не сможет, и смирился с наличием спутника."
    "The witcher understood that he couldn’t get out of it, and resigned himself to having a companion."

# game/script.rpy:4912
translate English choice_revenge_bee5b406:

    # "Совсем скоро товарищи оказались у Стрегобора в башне."
    "The comrades ended up in Stregobor`s tower."

# game/script.rpy:4923
translate English choice_revenge_bbb2f152:

    # "Stregobor""Добрые люди, рад вас видеть. С чем пожаловали ко мне?"
    "Stregobor""Good people, glad to see you. What have you come to see me for?"

# game/script.rpy:4924
translate English choice_revenge_38bcefae:

    # "Геральт всегда старался скрывать свои эмоции от собеседника, но в этот раз некоторая степень его волнения была видна."
    "Geralt always tried to hide his emotions from his interlocutor, but this time some degree of his excitement was visible."

# game/script.rpy:4925
translate English choice_revenge_53986767:

    # "Stregobor""Геральт, ты какой-то не такой."
    "Stregobor""Geralt, you`re somehow different."

# game/script.rpy:4926
translate English choice_revenge_178321c4:

    # "Stregobor""Что случилось?"
    "Stregobor""What happened?"

# game/script.rpy:4935
translate English choice_revenge_bdecb245:

    # "Geralt""Я уже это говорил, я недобрый человек!"
    "Geralt""I already said this, I am an unkind person!"

# game/script.rpy:4938
translate English choice_revenge_b2c6c890:

    # "В эту же секунду ведьмак достал свой кинжал из-за голенища и метнул его в сторону Стрегобора."
    "At that very second, the witcher took out his dagger from behind his boot and threw it towards Stregobor."

# game/script.rpy:4941
translate English choice_revenge_f38e5475:

    # "Колдун попытался среагировать, проговорив какое-то заклинание."
    "The sorcerer tried to react by casting some spell."

# game/script.rpy:4943
translate English choice_revenge_78fa788e:

    # "Вокруг него появился защитный купол."
    "A protective dome appeared around him."

# game/script.rpy:4955
translate English choice_revenge_f14f01ab:

    # "Кинжал отскочил от барьера и продолжил свой полет... "
    "The dagger bounced off the barrier and continued its flight..."

# game/script.rpy:4958
translate English choice_revenge_857e6f5a:

    # "Остановившись в груди Кальдемейна."
    "Stopping in Caldemeyn`s chest."

# game/script.rpy:4962
translate English choice_revenge_27ad0153:

    # "Геральт, не обратив внимания, достал свой меч из-за спины."
    "Geralt, not paying attention, pulled his sword from behind his back."

# game/script.rpy:4966
translate English choice_revenge_fe3c5954:

    # "И, сделав рывок, пронзил Стрегобора насквозь."
    "And, making a dash, pierced Stregobor through and through."

# game/script.rpy:4967
translate English choice_revenge_cf5479d1:

    # "В саду теперь стояло только одно живое существо."
    "There was now only one living creature standing in the garden."

